      "content": "That is a serious concern, and we appreciate you bringing this systemic bias to our attention for review. We understand the potential for inherent bias in current evaluation frameworks and agree that the high flagging rate for Global South researchers requires immediate attention. We are ready to collaborate fully on the recalibration next week to ensure the new metric fosters genuine cultural inclusivity while maintaining rigorous standards. Please let us know how we can best support the implementation process.",
